# Peaky Flexers — Docs & GitHub

When making changes to this project:

1. **Update documentation when relevant**
   - `templates/guide.html` — pedagogic user guide; update when inputs, outputs, or model logic change
   - `README.md` — project overview; update when features, defaults, or structure change

2. **Push to GitHub**
   - After committing changes, run `git push origin main` to sync with the remote repository
